[LANZHU]
If you're down, I'd love to do

00:00:18.810 --> 00:00:20.145 position:50% align:center line:84%
something like that again.

00:00:20.228 --> 00:00:23.273 position:50% align:center line:84%
Totally We should start
keeping a list

00:00:23.356 --> 00:00:27.485 position:50% align:center line:84%
of the incredible things the
13 of us can do together.

00:00:27.569 --> 00:00:29.237 position:50% align:center line:84%
[EMMA, KANATA laugh]

00:00:32.949 --> 00:00:34.826 position:50% align:center line:84%
This is huge, girls!

00:00:34.909 --> 00:00:38.872 position:50% align:center line:84%
Big news! This unofficial little
school idol club of ours

00:00:38.955 --> 00:00:42.375 position:50% align:center line:84%
